Package: htmxr.bootstrap
Title: Opinionated Bootstrap 5 Components for 'htmxr'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Arthur", "Bréant", , "arthur@thinkr.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Bootstrap 5 layer on top of 'htmxr'. Provides ready-to-use
    UI components — buttons, inputs, containers, cards, and more — with
    Bootstrap classes applied automatically. Part of the hyperverse
    ecosystem.
